28
00:04:13,311 --> 00:04:15,607
<font color="yellow">I'm so angry.</font>

29
00:04:27,422 --> 00:04:29,199
<font color="yellow">Let's see here.</font>

30
00:04:29,706 --> 00:04:31,985
<font color="yellow">I totally forgot to buy groceries.</font>

31
00:04:33,550 --> 00:04:36,581
<font color="yellow">It's all because of that crazy ghost.</font>

32
00:04:57,511 --> 00:05:00,773
<font color="yellow">Seriously though, where
