33
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:29,660
<font color="yellow">She's really nowhere in sight.</font>

34
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:33,201
<font color="yellow">Fine, I better not catch you.</font>

35
00:05:51,102 --> 00:05:53,814
<font color="yellow">You're still here.</font>

36
00:06:02,484 --> 00:06:05,300
<font color="yellow">Just where is my honey?</font>

37
00:06:05,300 --> 00:06:07,590
<font color="yellow">I know for a fact it's this school.</font>

38
00:06:07,591 --> 00:06:12,377
<font color="yellow">Honey! Honey! Honey, Honey! Honey!</font>

39
00:06:12,379 --> 00:06:16,115
<font color="yellow">Where are you, honey? Honey!</font>

40
00:06:28,787 --> 00:06:32,254
<font color="yellow">- Hi, Hyun Ji.
- Where have you been?</font>

41
00:06:32,256 --> 00:06:34,119
<font color="yellow">- Finding my honey.
- "My honey"?</font>

42
00:06:34,121 --> 00:06:35,268
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

43
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:38,585
<font color="yellow">It's been 30 years and I finally
found the man of my dreams.</font>

44
00:06:38,586 --> 00:06:41,138
<font color="yellow">I'm only going to follow him now.</font>

45
00:06:41,139 --> 00:06:42,449
<font color="yellow">You changed guys again?</font>

46
00:06:42,451 --> 00:06:44,689
<font color="yellow">You said that other guy was the
man of your dreams last time.</font>

47
00:06:45,526 --> 00:06:48,165
<font color="yellow">It's the real deal this time.</font>

48
00:06:48,901 --> 00:06:52,513
<font color="yellow">He's so tall and handsome.</font>

49
00:06:52,514 --> 00:06:55,386
<font color="yellow"><i>He was looking straight at
me with those dewy eyes of his.</i></font>

50
00:06:55,386 --> 00:06:57,025
<font color="yellow"><i>I got butterflies in my stomach.</i></font>

51
00:06:57,025 --> 00:06:59,547
<font color="yellow">Plus, he's pretty broad-shouldered.</font>

52
00:06:59,549 --> 00:07:01,653
<font color="yellow">He's perfect to cling on to.</font>

53
00:07:01,653 --> 00:07:03,763
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

54
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,929
<font color="yellow">What's the matter with you?</font>

55
00:07:07,699 --> 00:07:09,547
<font color="yellow">Did something happen?</font>

56
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,900
<font color="yellow">The thing is...</font>

57
00:07:18,636 --> 00:07:20,018
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

58
00:07:20,018 --> 00:07:25,749
<font color="yellow">So, it wasn't a soft and squishy
blood sausage, but that guy's lips?</font>

59
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:27,615
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

60
00:07:27,617 --> 00:07:31,122
<font color="yellow">Oh my gosh! I'm so jealous!</font>

61
00:07:32,064 --> 00:07:34,932
<font color="yellow">No, wait. So you kissed
that guy again, right?</font>

62
00:07:35,802 --> 00:07:37,754
<font color="yellow">Did you remember anything?</font>

63
00:07:46,110 --> 00:07:48,833
<font color="yellow">- No. Nothing!
- Nothing?</font>

64
00:07:48,835 --> 00:07:51,288
<font color="yellow">- Absolutely nothing?
- Yes!</font>

65
00:07:51,290 --> 00:07:55,155
<font color="yellow">I don't know what happened! Some
memories came back for sure last time.</font>

66
00:07:55,155 --> 00:07:57,233
<font color="yellow">How strange.</font>

67
00:07:58,810 --> 00:08:00,723
<font color="yellow">What should I do, Kyung Ja?</font>

68
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,376
<font color="yellow">Whom are you looking for?</font>

69
00:08:14,795 --> 00:08:16,554
<font color="yellow">Were you looking for me?</font>

70
00:08:17,436 --> 00:08:21,337
<font color="yellow">Hey, it's been a day since we've seen
each other. Aren't you happy to see me?</font>

71
00:08:21,338 --> 00:08:23,625
<font color="yellow">I'm very happy to see you.</font>

72
00:08:26,644 --> 00:08:29,438
<font color="yellow">- Come on, you're scaring me.
- "Come on"?</font>

73
00:08:30,111 --> 00:08:31,800
<font color="yellow">You really don't know?</font>

74
00:08:32,599 --> 00:08:35,800
<font color="yellow">You're shameless, selfish,
and arrogant to boot.</font>

75
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:39,722
<font color="yellow">Forget it. What would I
talk about with a ghost?</font>

76
00:08:45,458 --> 00:08:47,596
<font color="yellow"><i>Just stick to him
like glue no matter what.</i></font>

77
00:08:47,597 --> 00:08:50,142
<font color="yellow">Who knows? Your memories
might come back again.</font>

78
00:08:50,144 --> 00:08:51,765
<font color="yellow">You said he's an elite
college student, right?</font>

79
00:08:51,766 --> 00:08:55,750
<font color="yellow">Then ask him to help you with
your SATs. Do everything you can.</font>

80
00:08:56,699 --> 00:08:59,659
<font color="yellow">I'm pretty sure he's got something.</font>

81
00:09:00,599 --> 00:09:04,000
<font color="yellow">Bong Pal, wait for me!</font>

82
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:07,000
<font color="yellow">Bong Pal! Bong, Bong!</font>

83
00:09:08,383 --> 00:09:10,569
<font color="yellow">- How are you?
- Hello, Professor.</font>

84
00:09:10,570 --> 00:09:14,370
<font color="yellow">- What brings you here?
- Well... Professor.</font>

85
00:09:14,371 --> 00:09:18,622
<font color="yellow">About the dog you saved last time.</font>

86
00:09:19,199 --> 00:09:22,021
<font color="yellow">- Yes?
- May I take care of it?</font>

87
00:09:22,021 --> 00:09:26,054
<font color="yellow">Of course. That's perfect.
He hasn't met an owner yet.</font>

88
00:09:26,054 --> 00:09:29,746
<font color="yellow">Honestly, I saw him on the way here
and I can't stop thinking about him.</font>

89
00:09:29,747 --> 00:09:31,328
<font color="yellow">Ah, I see.</font>

90
00:09:31,329 --> 00:09:33,905
<font color="yellow">Can you come after class, then?</font>

91
00:09:33,906 --> 00:09:37,295
<font color="yellow">- Around three o'clock should be good.
- Yes, thank you.</font>

92
00:09:37,296 --> 00:09:40,900
<font color="yellow">It's a very happy day for him today.</font>

93
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:42,569
<font color="yellow">I'm already looking forward to it.</font>

94
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:49,719
<font color="yellow"><i>Say goodbye to love.</i></font>

95
00:09:52,309 --> 00:09:55,300
<font color="yellow"><i>You're back with me again.</i></font>

96
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:59,131
<font color="yellow">Hey, have you decided
not to speak to me?</font>

97
00:10:00,271 --> 00:10:02,914
<font color="yellow">I will help you.</font>

98
00:10:11,699 --> 00:10:13,723
<font color="yellow">Answer me!</font>

99
00:10:13,724 --> 00:10:15,799
<font color="yellow">- Hand it over.
- Will you forgive me if I do?</font>

100
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:18,180
<font color="yellow">- I said hand it over.
- No.</font>

101
00:10:29,050 --> 00:10:31,543
<font color="yellow">Hey, wait for me.</font>

102
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,221
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep following me?</font>

103
00:10:34,222 --> 00:10:36,053
<font color="yellow">I said I'll help you
get rid of the ghosts.</font>

104
00:10:36,054 --> 00:10:37,960
<font color="yellow">Do you honestly believe
I'll trust a ghost's word again?</font>

105
00:10:37,962 --> 00:10:40,774
<font color="yellow">Why not? I'm very trustworthy.</font>

106
00:10:40,775 --> 00:10:45,349
<font color="yellow">You're lying about your memories.
I know exactly what you're up to!</font>

107
00:10:45,351 --> 00:10:47,724
<font color="yellow">- I'm not lying!
- What is it, then?</font>

108
00:10:48,199 --> 00:10:50,506
<font color="yellow">What about your memories?
Did they come back?</font>

109
00:10:50,507 --> 00:10:54,376
<font color="yellow">- No... they haven't.
- See?</font>

110
00:10:54,376 --> 00:10:56,876
<font color="yellow">I was told not to believe
the words of a virgin ghost.</font>

111
00:10:58,646 --> 00:11:02,016
<font color="yellow">My memories popped up last
time, but not this time.</font>

112
00:11:02,017 --> 00:11:06,007
<font color="yellow">That's why I did what I did. I'm not
being sneaky, so please believe me.</font>

113
00:11:06,008 --> 00:11:08,901
<font color="yellow">- You're going to believe me, right?
- Then what?</font>

114
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:13,650
<font color="yellow">Your memories haven't returned,
so why are you agreeing to help me?</font>

115
00:11:14,099 --> 00:11:18,468
<font color="yellow">Well... I was wondering if you
can help me study for my SAT exam.</font>

116
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,050
<font color="yellow">- SATs?
- Yes.</font>

117
00:11:21,050 --> 00:11:23,900
<font color="yellow">You have to be pretty
smart to attend this school.</font>

118
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:25,796
<font color="yellow">Why would a ghost study for the SATs?</font>

119
00:11:25,798 --> 00:11:32,175
<font color="yellow">I don't remember, but I think I can't
cross over because I didn't take them.</font>

120
00:11:32,176 --> 00:11:35,421
<font color="yellow">I can't help but think that maybe I'll be
able to leave if I do well on my exams.</font>

121
00:11:38,755 --> 00:11:42,842
<font color="yellow">Please help me.
It's not hard to do.</font>

122
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:47,852
<font color="yellow">If you help me study, I'll pay
back the 10 million won I owe you.</font>

123
00:11:47,853 --> 00:11:50,775
<font color="yellow">Two million won per exorcism!
What do you think? A great idea, right?</font>

124
00:11:50,775 --> 00:11:52,690
<font color="yellow">It's one million won per ghost.</font>

125
00:11:52,692 --> 00:11:55,096
<font color="yellow">Then, 800,000 won?</font>

126
00:11:58,729 --> 00:12:01,045
<font color="yellow">500,000 won per ghost.
Take it or leave it.</font>

127
00:12:02,073 --> 00:12:05,195
<font color="yellow">I'll take it!
500,000 won per ghost it is!</font>

128
00:12:05,197 --> 00:12:07,500
<font color="yellow">Wait for me!</font>

129
00:12:07,639 --> 00:12:10,395
<font color="yellow">- Chun Sang, aren't you going to class?
- No, I'm not going.</font>

130
00:12:10,396 --> 00:12:14,049
<font color="yellow">Class is not important right now.
This punk is kicking my butt.</font>

131
00:12:14,969 --> 00:12:18,631
<font color="yellow">You've been at this since last night.
Give it a rest.</font>

132
00:12:18,631 --> 00:12:22,574
<font color="yellow">Nothing good will come out of it if
you keep messing with Sadako. He's evil.</font>

133
00:12:22,575 --> 00:12:25,126
<font color="yellow">You said he emptied out
your account several days ago.</font>

134
00:12:25,126 --> 00:12:27,256
<font color="yellow">Yes, he did. He bled me dry.</font>

135
00:12:27,256 --> 00:12:30,459
<font color="yellow">You call yourself my friend, yet you
have no loyalty and refuse to help me.</font>

136
00:12:30,460 --> 00:12:32,984
<font color="yellow">Just go and get your scholarship.</font>

137
00:12:32,986 --> 00:12:37,194
<font color="yellow">This Sadako needs
a taste of his own medicine.</font>

138
00:12:37,194 --> 00:12:40,806
<font color="yellow">He talked crap about me on the live
broadcast and now he's bullying me here!</font>

139
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:44,160
<font color="yellow">How dare he touch my pride!
You're so dead.</font>

140
00:12:44,161 --> 00:12:47,771
<font color="yellow">And he's the one who
uploaded that video!</font>

141
00:12:52,522 --> 00:12:56,628
<font color="yellow">Die, Sadako!</font>

142
00:13:11,689 --> 00:13:15,587
<font color="yellow">It used to be buy one get one
free. The promotion must be over.</font>

143
00:13:20,699 --> 00:13:21,948
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

144
00:13:21,949 --> 00:13:23,849
<font color="yellow">It's a toothbrush.</font>

145
00:13:23,851 --> 00:13:26,010
<font color="yellow">I know that, but why
are you putting it in here?</font>

146
00:13:26,011 --> 00:13:28,530
<font color="yellow">Because I need one
if we're going to be together.</font>

147
00:13:29,197 --> 00:13:31,142
<font color="yellow">Who said I'm going to
spend time with you?</font>

148
00:13:31,144 --> 00:13:34,194
<font color="yellow">- Put it back immediately.
- Why? We're a team now.</font>

149
00:13:34,195 --> 00:13:36,452
<font color="yellow">Some teams live together.
It's no big deal.</font>

150
00:13:36,453 --> 00:13:38,109
<font color="yellow">I don't live with ghosts, okay?</font>

151
00:13:38,109 --> 00:13:41,709
<font color="yellow">So you want me to go back and forth
slaying ghosts and studying?</font>

152
00:13:42,199 --> 00:13:44,813
<font color="yellow">It's more comfortable sticking
together, don't you think?</font>

153
00:13:45,699 --> 00:13:48,544
<font color="yellow">The truth is, I have no place to go.</font>

154
00:13:50,116 --> 00:13:52,497
<font color="yellow">Please! Please? Please?</font>

155
00:13:53,099 --> 00:13:57,895
<font color="yellow">Then including room and board...
it's 250,000 won per ghost.</font>

156
00:13:57,896 --> 00:13:59,828
<font color="yellow">250,000...</font>

157
00:13:59,828 --> 00:14:02,878
<font color="yellow">I'll never be able to pay
back the 10 million won!</font>

158
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:05,848
<font color="yellow">- Forget it then.
- Okay, okay! Deal.</font>

159
00:14:20,626 --> 00:14:22,899
<font color="yellow">- Excuse me.
- Yes?</font>

160
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:24,793
<font color="yellow">I'd like a mackerel, please.</font>

161
00:14:26,762 --> 00:14:29,450
<font color="yellow">- Here you go.
- Thank you. Have a good day.</font>

162
00:14:35,227 --> 00:14:38,163
<font color="yellow">Bong Pal, let's eat meat.</font>

163
00:14:39,943 --> 00:14:43,168
<font color="yellow">Meat! Meat! Meat!</font>

164
00:14:43,671 --> 00:14:45,482
<font color="yellow">Meat, my butt.</font>

165
00:14:45,482 --> 00:14:49,144
<font color="yellow">It's been a while since I ate meat.
We can use this to make some stew.</font>

166
00:14:49,145 --> 00:14:50,245
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

167
00:14:53,354 --> 00:14:55,189
<font color="yellow">- I said no.
- I want it.</font>

168
00:14:55,190 --> 00:14:56,670
<font color="yellow">No!</font>

169
00:14:56,671 --> 00:14:58,934
<font color="yellow">We're not eating meat!</font>

170
00:14:58,935 --> 00:15:01,906
<font color="yellow">- Let go.
- No.</font>

171
00:15:03,094 --> 00:15:05,149
<font color="yellow">I said let go!</font>

172
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:33,199
<font color="yellow">Meat. Delicious meat.</font>

173
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:35,741
<font color="yellow">I'm going to eat a lot of meat.</font>

174
00:15:35,742 --> 00:15:38,434
<font color="yellow">Are you happy? Because of you,
I'm overspending on living expenses!</font>

175
00:15:38,434 --> 00:15:40,434
<font color="yellow">You're going to eat it too.</font>

176
00:15:40,434 --> 00:15:42,966
<font color="yellow">Hey! Bong Pal!</font>

177
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:45,569
<font color="yellow">Can you buy me that dress?</font>

178
00:15:45,569 --> 00:15:47,503
<font color="yellow">To celebrate working together.</font>

179
00:15:47,990 --> 00:15:48,990
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

180
00:15:48,991 --> 00:15:52,747
<font color="yellow">I know that dress will look really
good on me. Don't you think so?</font>

181
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:57,099
<font color="yellow">No, I do not think so.
It won't look good on you at all.</font>

182
00:15:57,699 --> 00:15:59,591
<font color="yellow">No, look carefully.</font>

183
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:10,429
<font color="yellow">What do you think?
It's pretty, isn't it?</font>

184
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:22,675
<font color="yellow">Buy me this dress!</font>

185
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,603
<font color="yellow">He's always negative like that.</font>

186
00:16:27,604 --> 00:16:30,009
<font color="yellow">Wait for me!</font>

187
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,370
<font color="yellow">His eyesight is not that great.</font>

188
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:41,456
<font color="yellow">You'll have to bring him in at
least once a week for the time being.</font>

189
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,404
<font color="yellow">- Okay.
- Hold on.</font>

190
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:48,575
<font color="yellow">Okay.
Once in the morning and evening...</font>

191
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:52,599
<font color="yellow">Here, give this to him in
the morning and evening.</font>

192
00:16:52,599 --> 00:16:53,599
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

193
00:16:53,599 --> 00:16:56,162
<font color="yellow">It's time to say goodbye now.</font>

194
00:16:56,163 --> 00:16:58,147
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

195
00:16:58,148 --> 00:17:00,191
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

